How to downgrade firefox:
    The upgraded firefox problem: Cause the selenium driver cannot work properly.
 View the version of firefox in the system:
    $ sudo apt-cache show firefox | grep Version
# Install the corresponding verison:
    $ sudo apt-get install firefox=45.0.2+build1-0ubuntu1
# Keep current version and disallow updates
    $ sudo apt-mark hold firefox

# Unhold firefox verison and allows updates
    $ sudo apt-get unhold firefox
    $ sudo apt-get update


    
